\c 52 1 Muka, muka, iwe Zioni, uzvifu kidze nesimba rako; pfeka nguo dzako dzakaisvonaka, iwe Jerusaremu, guta dzvene; nokuti kubva zvino hakuna asina kudzingiswa noasakanaka angapinda mukati mako. 2 Zvizunze ubve muguruva; simuka, ugare kwazvo, iwe Jerusaremu; sunungura zvisungo zviri pamutsipa wako, iwe mukunda weZioni wakatapwa. 3 Nokuti zvanzi naJehovha "Makatengeswa kusina mutengo; muchadzikunurwa kusina mari." 4 Nokuti zvanzi naIshe Jehovha, "Vanhu vangu vakaburukira Ijipiti kare kundogarako, muAsiria akavamanikidza pasina mhosva. S Ko zvino
